			</tr><tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span>Ok,
<br />
So I tried kiting a few levels ago, around 28 or so (I'm 30 now).  I tried this is Marus Seru with Stonegrabbers.  I had a nice friend give me a SoW so that I didn't need to twist Selo's in.  I was twisting Brusco's Boastul Bellow, Denon's Disruptive Discord, and Selo's Consonant Chain.  I was able to stay ahead of my targets well enough, but they didn't seem to be losing any hitpoints.  I ran the same group of stonegrabbers around for probably 15-20 minutes and they were still above 90% health.  I ran a fairly tight circle around the mobs, even got close enough to be hit a few times, but they still weren't dying.  What am I doing wrong?</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
