				<td colspan="2"><span>Most lute's are secondary only.  Unless your have a great size bank account, you'll likely not be able to get ahold of an string instrument that is primary (like Lute of the howler).
<br />

<br />
Troubadors mace is secodary, but 1hb... meaning you can equip anther 1h primary weapon or a primary drum.
<br />

<br />
The few guides I ran across basically state.. if you get a lightcrawler, kick on selo's and head for the guards... then once the light crawler is dead, go back out and regain your kite, thus not completely losing/wasting all the time you put into the kite.  
<br />

<br />
Being 25 myself, can't help ya with the lvl 30 kiting places.. although, again , from the guides I read, they suggest trying to kite cougars in iceclad ocean.
<br />

<br />
Hope it helps.</span></td>
